high_descs: Turn to the left, and then the right and move back to the white table. Turn to the right and face it.
Pick up the knife from the center of the table.
Carry the knife and turn to the right, then the left and right again, to move back to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and then pick up the knife.
Hold the knife and turn to the right. Turn right again and move to the white table, and face it on the right side.
Place the knife on the right side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a knife and place it on the table.

high_descs: Go to the edge of the kitchen table ahead of you.
Grab a knife from the table.
Walk to the kitchen sink behind you.
Put the knife in the sink, wash it, then grab it.
Walk back to the kitchen table behind you.
Put the knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Wash a knife and replace it.

high_descs: Turn left at the fridge and face the side of the white table on the right.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle to the right of the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn right, head left to the stool and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the knife in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn right, head left at the fridge and face the side of the white table on the right.
Put the rinsed knife to the right of the head of lettuce on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed knife on a table.
